OL,5,Ccricket
OL,7,FA man from Telford has been told to
OL,8,Frepay #36,000 of benefit payments
OL,9,Fafter government investigators filmed
OL,10,Fhim playing cricket.
OL,12,FMembers of the Department for Work and
OL,13,FPensions' (DWP) fraud investigation
OL,14,Fteam say they filmed Shaun Rigby in
OL,15,F2023 playing cricket, walking and
OL,16,Frunning, bending down and standing up
OL,17,Fwith ease which they say contradict
OL,18,Fhis claims that he cannot walk five
OL,19,Fmetres without pain.
