OL,5,Ccricket
OL,7,FShaun was interviewed under caution in
OL,8,FAugust 2024 about suspected benefit
OL,9,Foffences and was told in August 2025
OL,10,Fthat he would not be entitled to
OL,11,Fbenefits.
OL,13,FShaun said: "I live my life through
OL,14,Fpain, I choose to get on with it
OL,15,Fbecause I want to live a normal life
OL,16,Fas I can whilst having a disability
OL,17,Fand it has been very difficult."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/8
