OL,5,Ccricket
OL,7,FHe added: "I have got medical evidence
OL,8,Fabout arthritis in my knee, bulges in
OL,9,Fthe bottom of my spine from the MRI
OL,10,Fscans but it doesn't seem to be enough
OL,11,Fand I'm thinking they want more, and
OL,12,Fmore and more, all because I was
OL,13,Fphysically active."
OL,15,FIn November, Shaun was told he does
OL,16,Fnot meet the requirements of the
OL,17,Fbenefits he receives following a
OL,18,Fmandatory reconsideration appeal.
