OL,7,FThe DWP then referred his case on to
OL,8,Fthe crown prosecution service, who say
OL,9,Fthey are considering whether Shaun
OL,10,Fshould be prosecuted.
OL,12,FThe sheet metal worker has received
OL,13,FPIP since 2016 and obtained a car
OL,14,Funder the Motability scheme three
OL,15,Fyears ago.
