OL,7,FShaun is supported by Disability
OL,8,FRights UK, who argue that the PIP
OL,9,Fmobility test is outdated and creates
OL,10,Fan "activity trap" where disabled
OL,11,Fpeople fear taking part in anything
OL,12,Fthat helps their wellbeing.
OL,14,FThe DWP said that Shaun was never
OL,15,Fentitled to the money and that now he
OL,16,Fmust repay it.
