OL,7,FIn a statement, it said an independent
OL,8,Ftribunal agreed with its decision and
OL,9,FPIPs were "awarded based on how a
OL,10,Fcondition impacts a person's day-to-
OL,11,Fday needs, as opposed to the condition
OL,12,Fitself".
OL,14,FIt added that: "We are committed to
OL,15,Fworking with anyone who is struggling
OL,16,Fwith their repayment terms, and our
OL,17,Fapproach balances the need to protect
OL,18,Fpublic funds by maintaining recovery
OL,19,Flevels, whilst providing a
OL,20,Fcompassionate service which considers
OL,21,Fsomeone's circumstances.
